ShortName: k-nearest neighbors
Topic: linear-algebra
Concepts: classify or predict by majority vote of k closest points,
 distance choice matters for kNN,
 choosing k (flexibility vs smoothness),
 the curse of dimensionality (high dimensions make all points far apart),
 when kNN works vs when it fails,
 kNN in R with class::knn()
BuildsOn: [distance-similarity-and-geometry](distance-similarity-and-geometry/lesson.qmd),
 [classification-evaluation](classification-evaluation/lesson.qmd) (soft — for reading confusion matrices),
 [model-fit-error-and-validation](model-fit-error-and-validation/lesson.qmd) (soft — for overfitting)
